# Project Licensing

This project uses a dual-license scheme. The hardware and firmware are licensed under different terms.

## Hardware License

The hardware designs, including schematics and PCB layouts, located in the `Hardware/` directory are licensed under the **CERN-OHL-S v2**.

A full copy of the license text is available in `Hardware/LICENSE`.

## Firmware License

The firmware applications, located in the `Firmware/` directory, are licensed under the **GNU Lesser General Public License v3.0 (LGPL-3.0)**.

A full copy of the license text is available in `Firmware/LICENSE`.
